  × onmouseover must be accompanied by onfocus for accessibility.
  
    5 │ <!-- onmouseover without onfocus -->
  > 6 │ <div onmouseover="handleMouseOver()"></div>
      │ ^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^
    7 │ 
    8 │ <!-- onmouseout without onblur -->
  
  i Actions triggered using mouse events should have corresponding keyboard events to account for keyboard-only navigation.
  

